"},{"pid":"806cf96c2af579dbdeaa92dad99ae0ff398b87ac","tid":1886271,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T21:13:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>火</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"19e3bef755a7357de9cafd488512a3df0712303a","tid":1886271,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T21:18:45.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"91a0f768a01bbce92cfebddeec75c13b57aade88","tid":1886271,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T21:18:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a96fef6e9a6dd04602044c523539b6b48330613d","tid":1886271,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"若上連登，就要有心理準備打輿論戰，連登是港府+ 中共關注的論壇，怎會不多政府人員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間會改過一切，我哋要有覺悟：連登已成戰場。<br />\n<br />\n若手足累了，要休息請放下電話，行山、煲劇、打機、聽歌，但不要懷著放鬆的心情看連登！（除非一群人自發用不推文模式之類）<br />\n<br />\n因為連登已成政府之刺，恨不得除之而後快！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知道一個人太崩緊會崩潰嗎？因此要休息。<br />\n其實，林鄭月娥最崩緊，最易崩潰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府最怕甚麼？  一定是<span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化，不割蓆，仲要擴大影響力的黃絲群體</span>"},{"pid":"b07ad7bd201392587e308007cdf837d42f72c962","tid":1886271,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T21:28:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0c32145fdf194658715a1b5c13b756cf24eef57","tid":1886271,"uid":207122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T22:34:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdeed216254b07084f34dc57931f6550a300e8a0","tid":1886271,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61814523b7daa5fbf21e6fb5d3a88eb683bfb829","tid":1886271,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":